description: {"blocks":[{"key":"ac1b6","text":"This is a \"how to\" step-by-step instruction for creating Projects and Designs in DIVA for automated design of oligos, plasmids and build instructions. User can either build plasmids on their own or submit the final Design for review/PI approval and third party (e.g., DIVA team) construction pipeline.
